channel.title: Comments on: REVIEW: Arctic Monkeys, Favourite Worst Nightmare, Domino

item.title: By: stevens_gerrard
item.dc:creator: stevens_gerrard
item.description: Just seen the them last night at Glastonbury, they were absolutely awesome, one of the best headline bands they've ever had at the festival! If not the best actually, they even did a cover of Diamonds are Forever. Absolute class!
